      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四太监引孙权同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙权",
          "line_type": "引子",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "南面称孤，镇江东，霸业鸿图。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙权",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "父兄征战有数年，开基创业在江南。曹操统领兵百万，要与孤家启争端。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙权",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "孤，孙权。承父兄之基业，坐镇江南，领守九州八十一郡。今有曹操，得了荆、"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙权",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "襄各郡，带兵百万，直下江南，有吞并东吴之意。昨日与群臣会议，文官个"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙权",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "个主降，武将大半要主战。倒叫孤家游疑不决。也曾修书去到柴桑，宣召周瑜，"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙权",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "等他到来再作商量便了。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（鲁肃上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "鲁肃",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "江北请卧龙，同来见主公。"
        },
        {
          "character": "鲁肃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "参见主公。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙权",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "大夫少礼。"
        },
        {
          "character": "鲁肃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "谢主公。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙权",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "今有曹操，遣使送来檄文；孤与众卿会议，文官主降，武将主战。不知大夫意"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙权",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "下如何？"
        },
        {
          "character": "鲁肃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "众人俱可降曹，惟主公则万万不可降曹。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙权",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "怎见得？"
        },
        {
          "character": "鲁肃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "鲁肃降曹，自然是加官受爵，封妻荫子；若主公降曹，位不过封侯，马不过一"
        },
        {
          "character": "鲁肃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "骑，从者不过数人，再想南面称孤，只怕不能够了！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（孙权笑。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙权",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "众人之言，大失孤望；大夫所议，正合孤心。但是那曹操，灭了袁绍，冀州兵"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙权",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "马皆为所得；近日又得荆、襄之众，其势甚大，恐难对敌。"
        },
        {
          "character": "鲁肃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "主公休要多虑。肃至江东，请得一人，乃诸葛瑾之弟，名诸葛亮。现到东吴，"
        },
        {
          "character": "鲁肃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "主公与他相见，定知曹操之虚实也。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙权",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "此人莫非就是那卧龙先生么？"
        },
        {
          "character": "鲁肃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "正是此人。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙权",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "他现在何处？"
        },
        {
          "character": "鲁肃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "现在驿馆。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙权",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "今日天色已晚，明日聚众文武于帐下，教他先看我江东之英俊，然后孤与他相"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙权",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "见便了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "鲁肃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "遵命。正是："
        },
        {
          "character": "鲁肃",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "欲图定国事，须问智谋人。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（鲁肃下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙权",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "待等明日，见了诸葛孔明，看他是怎样议论。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙权",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "退班！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（众人同下。）"
        }
      ],
      "interactions": [
        {
          "edge": "鲁肃→孙权",
          "turns": 8
        },
        {
          "edge": "孙权→鲁肃",
          "turns": 7
        }
      ],
