    {
      "scene_index": 4,
      "label": "第四场",
      "characters_present": [
        "孙权",
        "诸葛亮",
        "鲁肃"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四太监引孙权同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙权",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "曹操带兵下江东，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（鲁肃上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "鲁肃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "孔明先生到。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙权",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有请！"
        },
        {
          "character": "鲁肃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有请诸葛先生。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（〖牌子〗。诸葛亮上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "诸葛亮",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吴侯！"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙权",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "先生请坐。"
        },
        {
          "character": "诸葛亮",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "告坐！吾主刘玄德问候吴侯金安！"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙权",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "岂敢！久闻鲁子敬言道；先生躬耕南阳、抱膝隆中，有安邦定国之才。今幸相"
        },
        {
          "character": "诸葛亮",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不才无学，有辱重问！"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙权",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "先生曾在新野辅佐刘豫州与曹兵交战，必知曹营军情虚实。"
        },
        {
          "character": "诸葛亮",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "想那新野城池狭小，粮草不足；吾主刘豫州，兵微将少，寡不敌众，岂能与曹"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙权",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "曹操此番前来，不知兵将共有多少？"
        },
        {
          "character": "诸葛亮",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "马步水军，约有百万。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙权",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "百万兵将，恐是诈词。"
        },
        {
          "character": "诸葛亮",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "非诈也。想那曹操，据青、兖、幽、冀之兵已有二三十万；平了袁绍，又有五"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙权",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "但不知他帐下战将共有多少？"
        },
        {
          "character": "诸葛亮",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "他帐下足智多谋之士、能征惯战之将，至少也有一二千。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙权",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "今曹操平定荆、襄，但不知他尚有远图否？"
        },
        {
          "character": "诸葛亮",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "看他沿江下寨、准备战船、教练军士，不是取江东，他要取何处？"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙权",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "他既有吞并我江东之意，战与不战，愿先生与孤决之。"
        },
        {
          "character": "诸葛亮",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "亮有一言，恐吴侯不肯听从。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙权",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "愿闻高论。"
        },
        {
          "character": "诸葛亮",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吴侯要自己裁处。若以吴越之众，可与中原抗衡，不如早与之决；如其不能，"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙权",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "那刘豫州为何不降曹操？"
        },
        {
          "character": "诸葛亮",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "想昔日田横，乃齐之壮士，犹能守义不辱；况刘豫州乃帝室之胄，英才盖世，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（孙权愠怒。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙权",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "孔明大言，欺吾太甚！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（孙权下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "鲁肃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎呀！先生哪，你为何出此言？幸喜主公宽宏大量，不肯下责。你未免藐视吾"
        },
        {
          "character": "诸葛亮",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你主也太不能容物了。但我视曹兵，如拾草芥；你主不问，我故不言。"
        },
        {
          "character": "鲁肃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "如此，待我去请主公。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（孙权上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙权",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "何事？"
        },
        {
          "character": "鲁肃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "那孔明他言道，他有破曹之计。适才肃曾责备他来，他倒说主公不能容物。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙权",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "既然如此，待吾再去相见。"
        },
        {
          "character": "诸葛亮",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "亮亦出言冒昧，尚祈恕罪！"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙权",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "岂敢！想那曹操，生平所惧者：吕布、刘表、袁术、袁绍、玄德与孤。今日数"
        },
        {
          "character": "诸葛亮",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吴侯吓！"
        },
        {
          "character": "诸葛亮",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "说什么兵败新野城，"
        },
        {
          "character": "诸葛亮",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吾主帐下，关、张、赵云皆能勇敌万人，现有精兵两万；刘琦坐领江东，亦有"
        },
        {
          "character": "诸葛亮",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "先生之言，顿开茅塞！孤意已定：择日兴兵，共灭曹操也！"
        },
        {
          "character": "诸葛亮",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "听一言来喜在心，"
        },
        {
          "character": "诸葛亮",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "先生暂请回馆驿歇息。"
        },
        {
          "character": "诸葛亮",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "但凭三寸不烂舌，激动江东孙仲谋。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（诸葛亮下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙权",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "鲁大夫听者：待等公瑾到了南徐，命他与孔明相见，商议破曹之计。退班！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（孙权、四太监同下，鲁肃随下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（完）"
        }
      ],
